data.description: Step into a world of sophistication with completely custom woodwork, cabinets, countertops, and accent walls. The seamless fusion of design elements creates a unique ambiance throughout the home, setting it apart from the ordinary. The spacious layout encompasses 4 bedrooms, offering ample space for relaxation and rejuvenation. With 2 full bathrooms and 2 half bathrooms, convenience is at the forefront. Beyond the main living areas, enjoy additional entertainment space in the finished rec room, complete with bar. Whether it's a movie night or a game day, this versatile area caters to various leisure activities. Outside, escape to your private retreat on 5.76 acres, featuring a stocked pond for serene fishing days, over 1,000 planted trees enhancing the landscape, a sand volleyball court for recreation, a playground for family fun, and a dirt race track for the adventurous. Embrace the tranquility of country living while being conveniently close to local amenities and major commuting routes. Whether it's the custom interior, the recreational paradise, or the expansive acreage, this property is an absolute gem. Schedule a showing today and experience the perfect blend of modern living and outdoor recreation!
